author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Ingenico Group Q3 revenue 548 million euros, up 15 pct
text:
Oct 22 Ingenico Group :
* Q3 revenue 548 million euros ($611.68 million), up 15 pct
* Raises organic growth guidance to 12 to 13 pct vs 10 to 12 pct previously
* Raises EBITDA margin guidance to around 23 pct
